>docker-compose up -d
>docker-compose ps

>docker-compose exec ansible bash
from ansible container you should be able to ping other containers:
#ping 172.28.1.2  (or target1)
#ping 172.28.1.3  (or target2)
#ssh-keygen
#ssh-copy-id -i pi@171.28.1.2
#ssh-copy-id -i pi@171.28.1.2


to stop and remove containers:
>docker-compose stop
>docker-compose rm

